<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="pt">
  <head>
    <meta charset="utf-8" />
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1" />
    <meta name="robots" content="noindex, follow" />
    <title>Página não encontrada · Arcada</title>
    <link rel="icon" href="/favicon.svg" type="image/svg+xml" />
    <link rel="icon" href="/favicon.ico" sizes="any" />
    <style>
      :root { color-scheme: light dark; }
      html, body { height: 100%; margin: 0; }
      body {
        display: grid; place-items: center; padding: 2rem;
        background: #f6f3ed; color: #211c17;
        font-family: Georgia, "Times New Roman", serif;
        text-align: center; line-height: 1.5;
      }
      .mark {
        width: 56px; height: 56px; margin: 0 auto 1.5rem;
        color: #fd4f00;
      }
      h1 { font-size: clamp(2rem, 6vw, 3rem); margin: 0 0 0.5rem; letter-spacing: -0.02em; }
      p { color: #5b544d; margin: 0 0 2rem; max-width: 34ch; }
      a {
        display: inline-block; padding: 0.7rem 1.4rem;
        border: 1px solid #211c17; border-radius: 6px;
        color: #211c17; text-decoration: none; font-family: system-ui, sans-serif;
        font-weight: 600; font-size: 0.95rem;
      }
      a:hover { background: #211c17; color: #f6f3ed; }
      @media (prefers-color-scheme: dark) {
        body { background: #1c1813; color: #ede9e1; }
        p { color: #a39a8d; }
        a { border-color: #ede9e1; color: #ede9e1; }
        a:hover { background: #ede9e1; color: #1c1813; }
      }
    </style>
  </head>
  <body>
    <main>
      <svg
        class="mark"
        viewBox="0 0 32 32"
        aria-hidden="true"
        fill="currentColor"
        fill-rule="evenodd"
      >
        <path d="M6 27V13a10 10 0 0 1 20 0v14h-5V14a5 5 0 0 0-10 0v13H6Z" />
        <rect x="4" y="27" width="24" height="2.5" rx="1.25" />
      </svg>
      <h1>Página não encontrada</h1>
      <p>
        Esta página não existe ou foi movida. A lei continua a falar português — só noutro sítio.
      </p>
      <a href="/">Voltar ao início</a>
    </main>
  </body>
</html>
